|| **CC:** Operation Irenaeus ||
|| From: ##blue|DBAnna@PHYSICSDiv.goc##||

Undersecretary Al-Fine

We request an Immediate increase in funding and resources for all units in Operation Irenause.

Our estimations of the size and the number of personnel under the command of KTO-7890-Valentinus have been proven wrong. We are currently unable to attest the manpower of enemy forces, but we suspect it to be in the thousands. We request all members of, as well as phenomena related to, KTO-7890-Valentinus to be upgraded to Response Level 4 threats.

For further information, please consult the attached files

//Mundus, Normalis//

[[/div]]
[[=]]
[[div class="blockquote"]]
{{Opening ##blue|Archived_Operation_Irenaeus_Dossier_1.pto##...}}
[[/div]]
[[/=]]
[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-block
| name=https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/goc-ml/ion.jpg
| caption=Symbol recovered from a grimoire captured from KTO-7890-Valentinus
| width=200px]]
KTO[[footnote]] Known Threat Organisation[[/footnote]]-7890-Valentinus[http://scp-int.wikidot.com/sarkicism-hub  "Sarkic Church"][[footnote]] Also known as "Nälkä", Pan-Nälkä Congress and Sarkicism[[/footnote]] is an international millenarian religious movement of currently unknown origin and size, but presumed to be at least over 2500 individuals. The modification of organic material and the worship of a deity responsible for creation and destruction appear to be the main focus of the religion. All available evidence points towards it being composed of solely Type Yellow, Type Red and Type White humanoids. Members of KTO-7890-Valentinus are actively hostile towards operatives of the Global Occult Coalition and associated organizations.

**Structure:** The exact structure of KTO-7890-Valentinus is currently unknown, but presumed to be hierarchical. At least two positions of power are known to be recognized by its members, those being "Karcist" and "Ozi̮rmok". The former appears to correspond to Archbishops in the Catholic hierarchy, while the latter presumably denotes the movement's current leader.

**Resources:** Members of KTO-7890-Valentinus appear to be spread across both rural and urban areas around the world, with some holding secular positions of power. These include multiple pharmaceutical and biotechnology companies. The current economic and millitary power of KTO-7890-Valentinus is presumed to rival other KTO's, including KTO-0001-Bellfather.

**Standing Orders:** Members of KTO-7890-Valentinus are to be sought out and neutralized on sight. Due to the self-termination of past prisoners, attempts at apprehending living members have been rendered futile. Negotiations with KTO-7890-Valentinus operatives are forbidden.

[[/div]]

